howing upward trajectory - Checkmarks for: ✓ MVP Launched ✓ First Customers ✓ Marketing Active ✓ Sales Process ✓ Financial Model BOTTOM: Stats bar showing: \"84 hours invested | 42 AI agents deployed | 100+ deliverables created | 1 launched startup with revenue\" Use dramatic before/after contrast. Modern startup aesthetic with energetic colors on the right side, subtle animations implied (sparkles, motion lines). Inspirational and motivational tone. Let me try"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"[Content truncated — view full chat at source URL]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=4f35ab28-2433-4df9-a3b4-ce605b03f2bd","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=4f35ab28-2433-4df9-a3b4-ce605b03f2bd"}]}]}]
